PN,41901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe acting Vice Chancellor of the
OL,8,FUniversity of Kent says everyone in
OL,9,Fthe local community is "pulling
OL,10,Ftogether and looking out for each
OL,11,Fother" as the meningitis outbreak
OL,12,Fcontinues across the county.
OL,14,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV Meridian,
OL,15,FProfessor Georgina Ransley-Demora
OL,16,Fdescribed it as "a really really sad
OL,17,Ftime" at the university but said
OL,18,Feveryone is looking out for each other
OL,19,Fduring this "difficult time".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FHer interview comes as it was
OL,8,Fconfirmed the rollout of a meningitis
OL,9,FB vaccine to about 5,000 students
OL,10,Fliving on campus in Canterbury has
OL,11,Fbegun.
OL,13,FIn partnership with the UK Health
OL,14,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA), the
OL,15,Funiversity is rolling out vaccines to
OL,16,Fprotect students and is continuing to
OL,17,Foffer thousands of doses of
OL,18,Fantibiotics to students and staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"We've been working with public health
OL,8,Fauthorities, working through their
OL,9,Fprotocols to make sure we get people
OL,10,Fas safe as possible, as quickly as
OL,11,Fpossible", Prof Ransley-Demora added.
OL,13,F"As a university, we've also made some
OL,14,Fdecisions around assessments and exams.
OL,16,F"It's our exam period at the moment
OL,17,Fduring the university, so we've
OL,18,Fpivoted that online, but we've still
OL,19,Fgot support services available for the
OL,20,Fstudents here on campus, whether
OL,21,Fthey're anxious or uncertain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"And, indeed, we've got the antibiotic
OL,8,Ftreatment centre already up and
OL,9,Frunning, which has been so key,
OL,10,Foffering that potentially life-saving
OL,11,Ftreatment.
OL,13,F"I'm really proud of everybody pulling
OL,14,Ftogether at the university and in the
OL,15,Fpublic health authorities to get that
OL,16,Fup and running so quickly."
OL,18,FIt comes as five new cases of
OL,19,Fmeningitis have been reported in Kent,
OL,20,Ftaking the total number being
OL,21,Finvestigated by health officials to 20.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fsaid that 20 cases of meningitis had
OL,9,Fbeen reported to it, up from 15
OL,10,Fpreviously.
OL,12,FProfessor Ransley-Demora said the
OL,13,Funiversity is being guided by experts,
OL,14,Fand those experts are guided by the
OL,15,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"I think what everybody's recognised
OL,8,Fover the last few days is that the
OL,9,Fspread has perhaps been not as normal
OL,10,Fas it may have been, and, of course,
OL,11,Fthat will need to be reviewed in due
OL,12,Fcourse."
OL,14,FIt is unclear how students who have
OL,15,Falready left campus and have gone home
OL,16,Fto other parts of the country will
OL,17,Faccess a jab.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"What we need to do is make sure that
OL,8,Fthose that are on campus still in on-
OL,9,Fcampus accommodation are getting the
OL,10,Ftreatment they need from the
OL,11,Fantibiotic centre, and also that
OL,12,Fvaccination is available for those as
OL,13,Fthey've been identified as the target
OL,14,Fgroup.
OL,16,F"Our priority right now is making sure
OL,17,Fwe're providing what we need to for
OL,18,Fthe categories that have been
OL,19,Fidentified most at risk at the moment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"I'm reassured that the relevant
OL,8,Fpeople are considering what the next
OL,9,Fsteps might be in this programme, and
OL,10,FI'm sure the right decisions will be
OL,11,Ftaken."
OL,13,FA letter to University of Kent
OL,14,Fstudents said: "All students who
OL,15,Freside in Canterbury campus halls of
OL,16,Fresidence at the University of Kent
OL,17,Fare being offered the menB vaccine,
OL,18,Fwhich you can receive from 2pm today,
OL,19,FWednesday March 18.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"If you are onsite and unable to
OL,8,Freceive the vaccination today, the
OL,9,Fclinic will be open from 9am tomorrow,
OL,10,Fand the menB vaccine will continue to
OL,11,Fbe available to eligible students all
OL,12,Fweek.
OL,14,F"If you live in Canterbury campus
OL,15,Fhalls of resident but have already
OL,16,Freturned home, arrangements are
OL,17,Fcurrently being developed to ensure
OL,18,Fthat you can receive the vaccines
OL,19,Fnearer to home ` further information
OL,20,Fon how you can receive the vaccination
OL,21,Fwill be provided in due course."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773947499
OL,3,CUniversity of Kent: Meningitis spread
OL,4,Cis 'not normal' as vaccine rollout
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe university said the vaccination
OL,8,Fcourse contains two doses and
OL,9,Farrangements will be made for students
OL,10,Fto receive their second course of
OL,11,Ftreatment on the campus.
OL,13,FThe university added that alongside
OL,14,Fantibiotics offered, the menB vaccine
OL,15,Fis an "additional precautionary
OL,16,Fmeasure" available "to help protect
OL,17,Fstudents from becoming seriously
OL,18,Funwell with meningitis if you are
OL,19,Fexposed in the future".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
